Solving THE INDUSTRY's Urgent, Growing Needs

When it comes to evaluating brain data, objective evidence of any brain compromise is essential.

We combine cutting-edge brain injury science with legal expertise to streamline data collection and analysis for brain injury cases. By providing objective evidence of structural brain compromise, we help attorneys build stronger, more admissible cases.

Our Case Consultation service offers nationwide support, including gathering new data, reviewing client files, and delivering expert findings for admissibility motions—saving legal teams time and resources while navigating complex brain injury litigation.
